name: R4B-DiagnosticReport-R5-DiagnosticReport
title: Concept map to convert a FHIR R4B DiagnosticReport into FHIR R5

element.display: A Diagnostic report - a combination of request information, atomic results, images, interpretation, as well as formatted reports

target.display: A Diagnostic report - a combination of request information, atomic results, images, interpretation, as well as formatted reports
target.comment: R4B `DiagnosticReport` maps as Equivalent to R5 `DiagnosticReport`
R4B `DiagnosticReport.basedOn` maps as Equivalent to R5 `DiagnosticReport.basedOn`
R4B `DiagnosticReport.category` maps as Equivalent to R5 `DiagnosticReport.category`
R4B `DiagnosticReport.code` maps as Equivalent to R5 `DiagnosticReport.code`

R4B `DiagnosticReport.conclusion` maps as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget to R5 `DiagnosticReport.conclusion` - conclusion has change due to type change: R4B conclusion string has no equivalent or mapped type in R5 conclusion

R4B `DiagnosticReport.id` maps as Equivalent to R5 `DiagnosticReport.id`
R4B `DiagnosticReport.identifier` maps as Equivalent to R5 `DiagnosticReport.identifier`
